    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the car is sound with a steady engine and smooth transmission, though it shows expected signs of age and high mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery shows some wear and staining. It is a solid, honest car that performs its duties well but would benefit from some cosmetic attention.",
