    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation and care. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects an uncompromising commitment to excellence. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a specimen that remains in an exemplary state, devoid of mechanical or cosmetic imperfections. We invite you to experience a vehicle that sets the definitive standard for its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
